fine your hacking on the tasks that are explicitly free to hack</li>\\r\\n<li>If you find a cheat or trick to solve things more easily, please report it for Bonus Points</li>\\r\\n<li>The organizers might change the rules throughout the challenge. This will be announced on IRC</li>\\r\\n<li>Teams breaking these rules might be penalized or excluded from the competition</li></ul>\"}}'),(10,'PlaidCTF',10,'{\"ctftime\":{\"id\":10,\"url\":\"http://plaidctf.com/\",\"avg_weight\":82.6616666666667,\"description\":\"\",\"title\":\"PlaidCTF\",\"logo\":\"\",\"ctftime_url\":\"https://ctftime.org/ctf/10/\",\"slug\":\"plaidctf\"}}'),(11,'RuCTF Quals',11,'{\"ctftime\":{\"slug\":\"ructf-quals\",\"ctftime_url\":\"https://ctftime.org/ctf/11/\",\"logo\":\"https://ctftime.org/media/ctfs/a_5bc04ac0.jpg\",\"title\":\"RuCTF Quals\",\"description\":\"\",\"avg_weight\":53.3333333333333,\"url\":\"http://ructf.org/\",\"id\":11}}'),(12,'PHD CTF Quals',12,'{\"ctftime\":{\"slug\":\"12-phd-ctf-quals\",\"title\":\"PHD CTF Quals\",\"ctftime_url\":\"https://ctftime.org/ctf/12/\",\"logo\":\"https://ctftime.org/media/ctfs/cd56b95731708d5fb78c905d8ea7736b.jpg\",\"description\":\"All tasks are available here: http://ctfarchive.phdays.com/\",\"avg_weight\":53.3333333333333,\"id\":12,\"url\":\"http://quals.phdays.ru/\"}}'),(13,'PHD CTF Finals',13,'{\"ctftime\":{\"slug\":\"13-phd-ctf-finals\",\"ctftime_url\":\"https://ctftime.org/ctf/13/\",\"logo\":\"https://ctftime.org/media/ctfs/cd56b95731708d5fb78c905d8ea7736b_1.jpg\",\"title\":\"PHD CTF Finals\",\"description\":\"All tasks are available here: http://ctfarchive.phdays.com/\",\"avg_weight\":46,\"url\":\"http://phdays.com/\",\"id\":13}}'),(14,'ForbiddenBITS CTF',14,'{\"ctftime\":{\"slug\":\"forbiddenbits-ctf\",\"logo\":\"\",\"ctftime_url\":\"https://ctftime.org/ctf/14/\",\"title\":\"ForbiddenBITS CTF\",\"description\":\"\",\"avg_weight\":40,\"url\":\"http://ctf.forbiddenbits.net/\",\"id\":14}}'),(15,'Nuit du Hack CTF Quals',15,'{\"ctftime\":{\"title\":\"N